####################################################
Installation instructions for Benny_auto/Chooch_auto
Based on Benny-3.01\Chooch-4.01
####################################################

N.B. For autochooch you do not need PGPLOT library.
N.B. Before doing this you should have already installed the PGPLOT
library on your system

To install:

1. Download the distribution file Chooch_auto.tar.gz

2a. type gunzip Chooch_auto.tar.gz 
2b. tar xvf Chooch_auto.tar

3. cd Chooch-4.01/src

4. Edit the Makefile corresponding to your machine achitecture as instructed
   in the Makefile header.

5. Remove or rename any old versions of Benny and Chooch 
   in your bin directory

6. cd ../ and run the install script chooch-install.sh

7. Finally you will need to edit your site or personal .login file to
   define the environment variable CHOOCHDAT to point to the data directory
   under the Chooch-4.01 distrubution.<BR>
   e.g.  setenv CHOOCHDAT /usr/local/Chooch-4.01/data

8. Run the examples in the Chooch-4.01/examples directory and make sure everything is
   working correctly
